trans-unit.source: Contains information used to uniquely identify a manifest-based application.
This class cannot be inherited.
An application identity consists of the publisher's public key, the application name, the target processor architecture, the application culture, and the application version.
trans-unit.target: 应用程序标识组成发布服务器的公共密钥、 应用程序名称、 目标处理器体系结构、 应用程序区域性和应用程序版本。

trans-unit.source: The application identity properties values correspond to information contained in the application manifest.
trans-unit.target: 应用程序标识属性值对应于应用程序清单中包含的信息。

trans-unit.source: For more information about the application manifest, see [ClickOnce Application Manifest](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/29570cec-4e53-4660-a850-abc4fa150243).
trans-unit.target: 有关应用程序清单的详细信息，请参阅[ClickOnce 应用程序清单](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/29570cec-4e53-4660-a850-abc4fa150243)。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ApplicationId> is used by the <xref:System.Security.Policy.ApplicationSecurityInfo> class to identify a manifest-based application.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ApplicationId> 由<xref:System.Security.Policy.ApplicationSecurityInfo>类来标识基于清单的应用程序。

trans-unit.source: The following code example displays the <xref:System.ApplicationId> properties by obtaining the <xref:System.ApplicationId> from an <xref:System.Security.Policy.ApplicationSecurityInfo> instance created using the <xref:System.ActivationContext> for the currently executing manifest-based application.
trans-unit.target: 下面的代码示例显示<xref:System.ApplicationId>属性通过获取<xref:System.ApplicationId>从<xref:System.Security.Policy.ApplicationSecurityInfo>使用创建的实例<xref:System.ActivationContext>当前正在执行基于清单的应用程序。

trans-unit.source: The array of bytes representing the raw public key data.
The name of the application.
A <see cref="T:System.Version" /> object that specifies the version of the application.
The processor architecture of the application.
The culture of the application.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ApplicationId" /> class.

The constructor initializes the <xref:System.ApplicationId.Culture%2A>, <xref:System.ApplicationId.Name%2A>, <xref:System.ApplicationId.ProcessorArchitecture%2A>, <xref:System.ApplicationId.PublicKeyToken%2A>, and <xref:System.ApplicationId.Version%2A> properties of the <xref:System.ApplicationId>.
trans-unit.target: 构造函数初始化<xref:System.ApplicationId.Culture%2A>， <xref:System.ApplicationId.Name%2A>， <xref:System.ApplicationId.ProcessorArchitecture%2A>， <xref:System.ApplicationId.PublicKeyToken%2A>，和<xref:System.ApplicationId.Version%2A>属性<xref:System.ApplicationId>。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="name" /> is <see langword="null" />.
-or-
<paramref name="version" /> is <see langword="null" />.
-or-
<paramref name="publicKeyToken" /> is <see langword="null" />.
<paramref name="name" /> is an empty string.
Creates and returns an identical copy of the current application identity.
An <see cref="T:System.ApplicationId" /> object that represents an exact copy of the original.
The copy returned by this method is equal to the original as substantiated by the <xref:System.ApplicationId.Equals%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 此方法返回的副本是否等于原始如证实具有<xref:System.ApplicationId.Equals%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The hash codes for the original and the copy are also equal.
trans-unit.target: 原始数据库和副本哈希代码也是相等的。

trans-unit.source: Gets a string representing the culture information for the application.
The culture information for the application.
trans-unit.target: 应用程序的区域性信息。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ApplicationId.Culture%2A> value can include language information, for example, "en-US".
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ApplicationId.Culture%2A>值可以包括语言信息，例如，"EN-US"。

trans-unit.source: For information about culture values, see <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>.
trans-unit.target: 有关区域性值的信息，请参阅<xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>。

trans-unit.source: Gets the hash code for the current application identity.
The hash code for the current application identity.
This method generates the same hash code for two objects that have the same values for their <xref:System.ApplicationId.Name%2A> and <xref:System.ApplicationId.Version%2A> properties.

The name of the application.
trans-unit.target: 应用程序的名称。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ApplicationId.Name%2A> is the simple, unencrypted name of the application.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ApplicationId.Name%2A> 是应用程序的简单、 非加密名称。

trans-unit.source: Gets the target processor architecture for the application.
The processor architecture of the application.
trans-unit.target: 应用程序的处理器体系结构。

trans-unit.source: Valid values include "msil", "x86", "ia64", and "amd64".
trans-unit.target: 有效的值包括"msil"，"x86"、"ia64"和"amd64"。

trans-unit.source: The default is "msil", or Microsoft intermediate language, which means all your assemblies are platform independent, and the common language runtime will compile them when they are needed by your application.
trans-unit.target: 默认值为"msil"，即 Microsoft 中间语言，这意味着所有的程序集都是与平台无关，并且公共语言运行时将它们编译，在需要应用程序时。

trans-unit.source: Gets the public key token for the application.
A byte array containing the public key token for the application.
trans-unit.target: 包含应用程序的公钥标记的字节数组。

trans-unit.source: The public key token is represented by the last 8 bytes of the SHA-1 hash of the public key under which the application is signed.
trans-unit.target: 公钥令牌由在其下的应用程序签名的公钥的 sha-1 哈希的最后 8 个字节表示。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Reflection.AssemblyName.GetPublicKeyToken%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅<xref:System.Reflection.AssemblyName.GetPublicKeyToken%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>。
